### CP-001 — Consulta de saldo exitosa
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/1
X-API-KEY: IBM-HACKATHON-2026

### CP-004 — Acceso denegado (Sin API Key)
GET http://localhost:3000/accounts/1

### CP-009 — Transferencia exitosa (Happy Path)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": 1,
  "receiverId": 2,
  "amount": 100
}

### CP-013 — Transferencia rechazada (Fondos insuficientes)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "senderId": 1,
  "receiverId": 2,
  "amount": 5000

### BONUS: Health Check - Accounts Service
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### BONUS: Health Check - Processor Service
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### BONUS: Recarga de saldo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/recharge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 3,
  "amount": 500,
  "paymentMethod": "credit_card"
}

